==Untitled==
For some reason the comment didn't record on my edit. I changed [[University of Cincinnati]] [[Law School]] back to '''Cincinnati Law School''', redirecting to University of Cincinnati. The name is  the proper one. The U of C wasn't founded until [[1870]] and then absorbed several existing institutions, including the Cincinnati Law School. -- [[User:Decumanus|Decumanus]] 18:33, 2004 Nov 30 (UTC)

== How come he had so little success in his home state in 1892? ==
Weaver won neighboring Kansas, including most of the counties directly bordering Iowa, but didn't win even one county in his home state Iowa. How come? Please add this info if you have it. -- [[Special:Contributions/77.7.152.171|77.7.152.171]] ([[User talk:77.7.152.171|talk]]) 16:34, 22 May 2011 (UTC)

